  "original_title": "\u0dc4\u0dba\u0dd2\u0da7\u0dd2 \u0d85\u0d9c\u0db1\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0dbb \u0db4\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dad\u0dd2\u0dc0\u0dcf\u0daf\u0dd3 \u0d9a\u0dbd\u0dca\u0dbd\u0dd2 \u0d85\u0dad\u0dbb \u0d9c\u0dd0\u0da7\u0dd4\u0db8\u0dca\u0dc0\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dca 89\u0d9a\u0dca \u0db8\u0dbb\u0dd4\u0da7",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "89 killed in clashes between rival gangs in Haiti's capital",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "At least 89 people have been killed and many more injured in clashes between rival gangs in the Haitian capital, Port-au-Prince, the National Human Rights Protection Network said.",
        "The renewed violence comes amid rising food prices and fuel shortages, and the gangs are said to be emerging as the city's security situation worsens.",
        "Violence erupted on July 7 between two rival factions in a poor and crowded neighborhood of Port-au-Prince.",
        "At least 89 people were killed and 16 others are missing in this attack. Another 74 people were shot or stabbed, NGOs said.",
        "International humanitarian organizations have also had to put in a lot of effort to provide essential food supplies and medical treatment to the victims in the affected areas.",
        "In this situation, it is reported that a large number of people have difficulties in getting food or health facilities."
      ],
